templates
- mail_recovery_subject
    name: mail_recovery_subject
    type: text
    data|text
      text: Password recovery on %%_domain
- mail_recovery_body
    name: mail_recovery_body
    type: text
    data|text_multiline
      delimiter: &#10;&#10;
      text
      - 2: You received this message because someone tried to recover the password from your account on %%_domain.
      - 4: Your new password on %%_domain was changed automatically to: %%_new_password
      - 6: Your EMail is not shown publicly on %%_domain and it is never shared with third parties!